data.description: ***This home is offering a 1 year mortgage rate buy down with our preferred lender. Your mortgage rate will be 1 point less than the current market rate for one year. This home also has a recent appraisal at $1,050,000. ***  Welcome to your dream lake house at 20345 Moss Bend Ct, Lutz, Florida. This magnificent home offers the perfect blend of luxury, privacy, and serene waterfront living. Boasting just under 3,500 square feet of living space, this 2-story residence is situated on an expansive 1.6-acre lot with no HOA rules or community development district fees.     This spacious home is designed for comfort and functionality, providing ample room for family and guests.     Enjoy the best of waterfront living on Moss Lake, a pristine ski lake that welcomes motor ski boats. Dive into endless water sports and create lasting memories with family and friends.    Your privacy is paramount with the property offering security with a front entrance gate and a sense of exclusivity.    The breathtaking West-Facing Sunset Views allow you to indulge in the captivating beauty of Florida sunsets right from your backyard. Watch as the sun dips below the horizon, casting a warm, golden glow over the tranquil waters.     The house features a well-designed open floor plan, perfect for entertaining. The primary suite is conveniently located on the first floor for added convenience and relaxation. There is also an intercom system throughout the entire house that allows you to communicate with anyone in any room.    Nestled in the heart of nature, this property offers a rare sense of seclusion and tranquility, allowing you to escape the hustle and bustle of daily life.    This lakeside paradise is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle. Imagine waking up to the calm lake, spending your afternoons on the water, and winding down with breathtaking sunsets. Your private escape awaits at 20345 Moss Bend Ct.    Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a piece of Florida's waterfront paradise. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the beauty and serenity of this lakefront gem in Lutz. Your dream home on Moss Lake is just a phone call away.
